{"tid":808182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠市況逆轉前甩手","createTime":"2018-09-06T06:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T07:17:55.000Z","uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21b6f84fc891bcfb9086a1f22e839121707b7a1b","tid":808182,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠眼光向來精準，多個中資財團早已垂涎中環中心，出價由300億元開始，最終去年11月拍板，以402億元，每呎3.3萬元出售，是李嘉誠退休前的最後一單大刁。<br />\n<br />\n多次「聞到味」避災<br />\n<br />\n去年7月李嘉誠先賣和電固網、再賣中環中心、北角和富薈、重慶地皮，對後市似乎不樂觀。一班中環中心投資者在購入半年後，雖曾以高達每呎5萬元拆售，惟中環中心易手至今不足一年，市況已開始逆轉。李嘉誠若將中環中心持有至今，能否將物業近乎全幢脫手也成疑問。<br />\n長和（001）執行董事兼公司秘書施熙德曾接受訪問，指今年她為李嘉誠撰寫「主席前瞻」，尚未有人對貿易戰警惕之時，李嘉誠已要求她在「主席前瞻」中加上貿易戰這議題。作為長和秘書，施熙德或有拍馬屁之嫌，但回看李嘉誠的戰績，67年暴動、89年六四，人心惶惶之際，李嘉誠大量吸納低價地皮，亦多次「聞到味」避開股災，於1987年股災前大供股，1997年亞洲金融風暴前重組，2015年大時代爆煲前世紀重組。<br />\n長實前日回購180萬股，涉資1億元，同系長和昨日亦回購60萬股，涉資近5,460萬。兩股昨日分別升4.775%及3%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180905&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20492571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180905%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20492571&d=w5pgVsCMpZrOvdE%2B8kmc8k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=099356b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180905%26sec_id%3D15307%26s%3D0%26a%3D20492571&h=a9a0c65f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180905&amp;sec_id=15307&amp;s=0&amp;a=20492571</a>"},{"pid":"f05b6844d2e5ba266dafc861a9a008290c17a40c","tid":808182,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"留名等睇有人叫誠哥呢種「專家」食屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be45ac5d5ec190faab811aea69520ffd48babdd","tid":808182,"uid":156911,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8047367b3ae595c685ce0afb287585cf2bb2889","tid":808182,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"收到風姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有次次都咁準"},{"pid":"426b4510383c021245b6a6c00f1e976308525ceb","tid":808182,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a3c1c2cb340356139012b33224aedf7191960a9","tid":808182,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【商廈拆售】中環中心連環沽散位 本地用家1.67億掃入自用</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180906/large/1536214163_85ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180906%2Flarge%2F1536214163_85ae.jpg&h=437e6af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資深投資者蔡志忠拆售中環中心22樓全層，今天録連環成交，分別為2212及2213室，合共約3,941方呎，成交價約1.669億元，呎價約42,340元。據了解，買家為本地用家，租用同區甲廈多年，看好甲廈前景，供平過租，於是購入自用。<br />\n<br />\n中環中心22樓推出9個單位，一個月內售出6個單位。蔡志忠表示，餘下2205及2208室將於短期加價，預期潛在加幅約3%。"},{"pid":"58af6e52c53793e059de76c656b349ea3da3172c","tid":808182,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"其實之前都有人睇到個市開始唔掂<br />\n係+x真係敢走"},{"pid":"c9226a8828592a72214c5ff2fd274145b7722017","tid":808182,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠十幾年前已經走緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1859f6344da26906b98cceaae714269f9c0f7982","tid":808182,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"誠哥: 加拿大先係我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4740da06774720f699982af9235047a907a2c27","tid":808182,"uid":11472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"佢玩咁多味,淨睇大數據都夠做"},{"pid":"130e3a0992350dc1b20fbe536b7bf3caa80acb89","tid":808182,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f05b6844d2e5ba266dafc861a9a008290c17a40c","tid":808182,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"留名等睇有人叫誠哥呢種「專家」食屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"誠哥玩實戰 d專家得理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}